    <briefdescription>
<para>CANopen CiA 302 Network Manager, SDO Client &amp; NMT Master. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a lightweight, non-blocking CANopen master engine capable of transmitting NMT node control commands, executing expedited/segmented SDO reads &amp; writes to remote slave nodes, and monitoring network heartbeats. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
